{"tid":424580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇男為民除害　與7公尺巨蟒搏鬥爆血重傷","createTime":"2017-10-05T00:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T18:10:47.000Z","uid":63669,"like":315,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"18b90680e0301e7a7e0e54c31dbbbbde2497ae75","tid":424580,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"印尼廖內省(Riau)一名37歲英勇男子那巴班(Robert Nababan)為民除害，他在路上與一隻長達7公尺的巨蟒搏鬥，最後那巴班獲得勝利，但也身受重傷，目前正在醫院治療中。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，那巴班日前從棕櫚油植栽場下班回家，卻在路上發現有兩名路人被這隻巨蟒圍困，那巴班見義勇為，立刻發揮為民除害之心。那巴班上前與巨蟒搏鬥，完全不懼怕這條龐然大物，最後那巴班獲得勝利，巨蟒被他殺死，但那巴班也身受重傷，隨後被送醫治療。<br />\n那巴班說，他在與巨蟒搏鬥時，手臂遭到巨蟒狠狠攻擊，而他繼續和巨蟒纏鬥。目前那巴班的手臂傷勢嚴重，體力也耗盡，正在醫院接受治療，而死去的巨蟒則成為村裡的展示品、孩子的玩具。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mn7kwpg0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmn7kwpg0&h=9e8d4c64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f3376db16c677f30c6e100678c90afc206c9f97","tid":424580,"uid":17032,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個蛇頭大到咁"},{"pid":"ccdd4d28246c06cc12419c55b841173c8c8b05e4","tid":424580,"uid":23451,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:45:09.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f7e54ca4aa9cf24b764546c50931040ce8341b","tid":424580,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁大條"},{"pid":"b75ce9aabdae01b5775b97231899460352728806","tid":424580,"uid":123969,"like":495,"dislike":3,"score":492,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:50:25.000Z","msg":"沒有遊戲機也能玩魔物獵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae980465dc0087865336b4b7c63c563b74b0cf52","tid":424580,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T00:52:00.000Z","msg":"<im